---
title: Cajun-inspired Bell Pepper Linguine with golden cheese and creamy tomato sauce
description: This fusion pasta dish is spiced with an exciting array of Cajun flavours and topped with fresh chilli for added optional bite. It also features tender pan-fried peppers and golden grilling cheese making for a delicious meal that pulls inspiration from a myriad of different destinations.
